{"tid":121071,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【中學作文】假設你是七警之一，試描述入獄生活（不得多於三句）","createTime":"2017-02-15T02:44:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-15T14:05:06.000Z","uid":69866,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d05cd46e2bb6c8a51f9407a9d6ee2dd2b049c819","tid":121071,"uid":69866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T02:44:13.000Z","msg":"【中學作文】假設你是七警之一，試描述入獄生活（不得多於三句）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 我遇上了我親手拘捕的人，他是一個GAY佬，我很害怕，所以我不會沖涼。<br />\n2. 入獄第三天，我女朋友終於肯黎見我，好開心。<br />\n3. 我女朋友黎見我同我講政府收番左宿舍，冇得住，要同我分手，好傷心。"},{"pid":"29566419fad73c8a26f53d0d89d40f43dce6232e","tid":121071,"uid":41742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T02:48:35.000Z","msg":"我地無做錯到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9cbe1b02e14e70de843298082ecb053f84342fe","tid":121071,"uid":69866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T03:00:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我地無做錯到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n4. 我地某位同袍每日高呼「我地無做錯到」，佢菊花日日都唔得閒。<br />\n5. 捨己為人既精神真係好值得鼓勵。<br />\n6. 於是我同佢一齊大叫「我地無做錯到」。"},{"pid":"ea76d7bfb683bfa50dde609e252f5b5ce758841c","tid":121071,"uid":3611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T03:36:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f1ff7204972932989bf18d9e6bc5b84ba7ecb159","tid":121071,"uid":49,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T03:44:04.000Z","msg":"1有4句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86eb8af4c8e855d00036ad861af409bda2519594","tid":121071,"uid":49,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T03:44:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1有4句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自隊1打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" cla